		<p>Project Spy is a simple no-frills lane-based task management app.</p>

		<div class="col-2">
			<div>
				<p>It keeps tasks within a project, as markdown files, instead of with a disconnected service.</p>
				<p>Local tasks and notes makes finding tasks and information, committing task alongside code creates a better context around the work outside reading through version control log messages.</p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h4>Features</h4>

				<ul>
					<li>Keep your tasks in your project repository</li>
					<li>Add notes and ideas</li>
					<li>Quickly find tasks</li>
					<li>Filter tasks by tags</li>
					<li>Promote tasks with priority and order</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
{{ end }}
